  Privacy Policy for GoldInvoice 

            Last Updated: 14/01/2024

            1. Introduction

            Welcome to [Your App Name]! This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information. By using [Your App Name], you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

            2. Information We Collect

            2.1 Personal Information

            In the course of using our app, we may collect the following personal information:

                Name
                Phone number
                GST number
                Shop name
                Address

            2.2 Usage Information

            We also collect non-personal information about how you interact with our app. This may include:

                Device information (e.g., device type, operating system)
                Log data (e.g., IP address, access times)
                Usage patterns and preferences

            3. How We Use Your Information

            We use the collected information for the following purposes:

                To create bills for gold shops as per the app's primary functionality.
                To communicate with you regarding your account and app-related updates.
                To improve our app's features and user experience.
                To comply with legal and regulatory requirements.

            4. Data Security

            We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.

            5. Sharing of Information

            We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as described in this Privacy Policy or as required by law.

            6. Your Choices

            You can review and update your personal information within the app settings. If you wish to delete your account, please contact us at [goldinvoice0@gmail.com].

            7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

            We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. The updated version will be indicated by the "Last Updated" date at the beginning of the policy.

            8. Contact Us

            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [goldinvoice0@gmail.com].

            Thank you for using GoldInvoice!
